# Auto publish

**Always publish.** After finishing any fix or feature, immediately commit and push to `origin/main` without asking.

- Do not ask «انشر؟» or wait for approval — publish by default.
- Follow git safety: no force push, no secrets, clear commit messages.
- Only skip push if the change is explicitly local-only or the user said not to publish that item.
